data.title: ELI No. 16-2015 PDF
data.meta_description: ELI No. 16-2015.pdf - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document contains proceedings from the 12th International Conference of the Faculty of Letters at the University of Pitești held from June 12-14, 2015. It includes papers on various topics related to Romanian language and literature, presented in Romanian, French and English. The proceedings were published with financial assistance from the Agence Universitaire de la Francophonie under the high patronage of the University of Pitești.
